data.title: Duke Karl Theodore of Bavaria
data.meta_description: THE subjoined extract from the official gazette of the Principality of Monaco, referring to the death of Duke Karl Theodore of Bavaria, is worthy of being put on record as an appreciation of one great personage of high rank by another, and an acknowledgment that the nobility of station which commands the greatest respect is that which carries with it personal service to the community.
